collectionData.title: KGF-2 actress Srinidhi Shetty stuns in a mint green anarkali
collectionData.intro: Anarkali suits are back to rule the summer and how! Mostly stitched as a long, frock-style kurta, these suits usually have a slim fitted bottom and vary in length and embroidery, but are mostly stitched with floor-length cuts. With Bollywood and Tollywood celebrities wearing them again this season, they are set to become an eternal piece of summer clothing. And the latest diva to rock it in style is none other than former beauty queen and Telugu actress Srinidhi Shetty. The actress left us impressed in her recent anarkali outing and if you love these flowy kurtas, you ought to checkout Srinidhi's anarkali.
